{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_10_01",
  "title": "兵藤雫 1話 主役のアリスだよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『劇団★見』結成後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—After the formation of “Troupe★Hoshimi”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、ここは……もう少し、動作を大きくした方が\n映えるかも……もう一回やってみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ here… Maybe making the movements a bit bigger\nwould make it stand out more. Let’s try it one more time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　{user}さん、お疲れ様、です\nごめんなさい、集中してて気付かなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? {user}-san‚ good work.\nSorry‚ I was so focused I didn’t notice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫も演技の練習、お疲れ様\n劇団★見での活動、始めてみてどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work on your acting practice too‚ Shizuku.\nHow is it‚ now that you’ve started activities with Troupe★Hoshimi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく、楽しい……！\nでも、やることも考えることも一杯で、大変",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s really‚ really fun…!\nBut there’s so much to do and think about‚ it’s tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9074147225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "どの演目をやるのか決める時も……\nみんなと一緒に、凄く悩んだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when deciding which play to perform…\nI really struggled over it with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.1740813892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、すずちゃんと偶然本屋さんで会って……\nお互いに好きなお話が一緒で、ちゃんと選べた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then I happened to run into Suzu-chan at a bookstore…\nand we liked the same story‚ so we could choose properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2018596251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "大変だけど、一人じゃないから\n充実してて、楽しい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s tough‚ but I’m not alone‚\nso it feels fulfilling and fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8407480558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "順調そうだな。雫はよく頑張ってると思うよ\n座長としても、役者としても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds like things are going well. I think you’re doing great‚ Shizuku.\nBoth as the troupe leader and as an actress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "実は演技……すみれちゃんに頼んで、見てもらってる\n『ぱじゃパ！』がきっかけで、仲良くなったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ for my acting… I asked Sumire-chan to watch me.\nWe got close because of “Pajama Party!”‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8827433904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "あの『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』の舞台に立った憧れの\n名優さんに稽古をつけてもらうなんて……凄く贅沢",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so having the actress I admire\nfrom the “Pretty ★ Angel” stage coach me… it’s such a luxury.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8160767238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "見てくれるだけじゃなく……練習方法も、教えてくれる\n私の演技、良くなったのは……アドバイスのおかげ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She doesn’t just watch—she teaches me practice methods too.\nMy acting has improved… thanks to her advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6494095485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すみれの指導つきか。それは心強いな\nそれにしても、今回の雫はいつになく積極的だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Guidance from Sumire‚ huh. That’s reassuring.\nStill‚ you’re unusually proactive this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "そうかも……やっぱり『ぷりエン』の舞台を観て\n感動したのが大きい。演じたい気持ち、メラメラしてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe… watching the “Pretty ★ Angel” stage\nreally moved me. My desire to act is burning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2157427055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "演目の台本、優ちゃんが書いてくれたんだけど……\n普段自分では言わないようなことも、演技だと、言える",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan wrote the script for the play‚ and…\neven things I’d never say on my own‚ I can say when I’m acting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.98886114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "優は普段から話運びや言葉選びがうまいからな\nたまに過激だけど……。これが優の書いた台本か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu’s always good with flow and word choice.\nSometimes a bit extreme‚ though… Is this Yu’s script?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9666631063,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5948.981277299992,
          "startTime": 127.9156443836
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6833.333333400006,
          "startTime": 128.7999964397
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どれどれ……今回は大丈夫だな。さっき練習してたのは\n台本のこのシーンか。雫の演技、凄く自然だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see… this one’s fine. What you were practicing earlier\nwas this scene‚ right? Your acting felt very natural.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1999964397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……まだまだだけど、頑張る\n本番で『まだまだ』、なんて思いたくないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu… I’m still not good enough‚ but I’ll do my best.\nI don’t want to think “I’m not good enough” during the real thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6640085858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも今日は朝からずっと練習漬けだったんだろ？\n少しくらい休憩をとった方がいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you’ve been practicing nonstop since morning‚ right?\nYou should take at least a short break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.933329773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "……忘れてた。そうだね、少し……休憩する\n{user}さんは、もうお仕事戻っちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I forgot. You’re right‚ I’ll… take a short break.\n{user}-san‚ are you going back to work already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.6901531539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……良かったらこのまま、雫が劇団を\n立ち上げた理由をもう少し聞きたいんだけど、いいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… if it’s okay‚ I’d like to hear a bit more about\nwhy you started the troupe. Would that be alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4999964397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "うん。じゃあ一緒に休憩、しよ。……嬉しい\nちょっと、着替えてくるから……少し、待ってて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Then let’s take a break together… I’m happy.\nI’ll go change real quick… please wait a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.6738945327,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.0378659807
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.0378659807
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "私が、劇団を立ち上げたきっかけは……\nトリエルとfranさんの舞台を観たからなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason I started the troupe was…\nbecause I watched TRINITYAiLE’s and fran-san’s stage play.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.9072278661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』の舞台か……\nトリエルの三人が主演のあの舞台、いい出来だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The “Pretty ★ Angel” stage‚ huh…\nThat play starring the three from TRINITYAiLE was well done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.8738947553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 196.9031038844
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "第二弾では、悪役としてfranさんも出演して……\n思い出すと、うっ、胃が……。舞台は面白かったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the second installment‚ fran-san also appeared as a villain…\nJust remembering it—ugh‚ my stomach… the play was great‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.4805866201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "うん、凄く面白かった……！\n第一弾も良かったけど、さらに、パワーアップしてた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it was really amazing…!\nThe first one was good too‚ but it was even more powerful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.5187864846,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 213.6065215671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "特に、franさんの演技が良かった……\n悪役、似合ってた。ハマり役",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fran-san’s acting was especially great…\nThe villain role suited her perfectly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.9868578596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "私、原作のアニメを履修してから観に行ったけど\n……キャラへの理解度が、半端じゃなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I watched it after studying the original anime‚ but…\nher understanding of the character was incredible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.2625064238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 227.3711927339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな。裏ではいろいろあったけど……\nでも、劇団を立ち上げた理由は、それだけなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True. A lot happened behind the scenes‚ though…\nStill‚ was that the only reason you started the troupe?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.5409573131,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "聞いたぞ。配役を決める時、主役の座をすずと\n張り合ったんだって？　随分積極的じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard that when deciding roles‚ you competed with Suzu\nfor the lead. That’s pretty proactive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.4999903362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 243.4791288619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "うん、どうしても主役……アリス役、やりたかったから\n私、あまり前に出るタイプじゃないし……やっぱり変？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I really wanted to play the lead… the role of Alice.\nI’m not really the type to step forward… is it strange?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.0738865219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 256.5191288238
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
