      "text": "そんなことはないよ\nだけど、主役に立候補した理由は聞きたいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all.\nBut I did want to know why you volunteered for the lead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.4999903362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_10_01-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "理由は、いろいろある。けど一番の理由は、昔の心残り\n……恥ずかしくて、みんなには話してないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are many reasons‚ but the biggest is a regret from the past.\n…It’s embarrassing‚ so I haven’t told everyone‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.806017876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 274.4572467094
    },
    {
