      "text": "誰がどの役をやるのか、決める時……\n先生と目が合って……やってみないか、って言われて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we were deciding who would play which role…\nI made eye contact with the teacher… and she suggested I give it a try.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.8873944286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
