      "text": "「私、劇でアリスをやる」って\n「不思議の国のアリスの、主役のアリスだよ」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I’m playing Alice in a play‚”\n“Alice‚ the lead from Alice in Wonderland‚” I said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 333.1207277619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 337.2847907308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
